{"tid":1192352,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"香港啲巴士站等巴士同用廢氣謀殺有咩分別","createTime":"2019-06-08T11:29:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-08T11:29:29.000Z","uid":63154,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9ac38953d5f00074d3a0de661285da334b3fb402","tid":1192352,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:29:00.000Z","msg":"香港環境太特殊，巴士班次密，路面本身已經超級繁忙，留意到巴士個設計有個好大問題，死氣喉竟然係靠左，靠向巴士站噴而唔係靠路中心噴，個站露天空曠都還好，但遇啱條街兩邊都圍住高嘅建築物，死氣係困住係成條街，旺角雅蘭中心門口就係好例子，更差嘅情況係室內有蓋巴士站，好心加多幾把大風扇帶啲廢氣出室外啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實每日搭巴士返工嘅你有冇去照吓肺？要定期檢查呼吸系統喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cdf1871631c1c45b8ff00e51a21385f16a7e746","tid":1192352,"uid":28366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T11:29:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/PoliticalVigorousHousefly-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FPoliticalVigorousHousefly-size_restricted.gif&h=41e34efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62013711_659215344521877_1086940503313743872_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=12470952d62fcbd0e5fc1c4e9fee3127&amp;oe=5D99AB8B\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62013711_659215344521877_1086940503313743872_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D109%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D12470952d62fcbd0e5fc1c4e9fee3127%26oe%3D5D99AB8B&h=ca0db275&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}